    "The percentage scores (mean and standard deviation) of the LLMs' responses on the RD exam questions.",
    "obtained higher average errors for the Difficult and Expert level questions.",
    "RAP obtained higher error rates for Moderate and Difficult questions.",
    "The inaccurate responses collected by each approach is evaluated based on four domains: D1) Principles of Dietetics, D2) Nutrition Care for Individuals and Groups, D3) Food Service Systems, and D4) Management of Food and Nutrition Programs and Service.",
